			var src ="//in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/website/banner/large/jhootha-kahin-ka-et00105933-27-06-2019-07-04-59.jpg", imgSrc = "//in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/website/poster/large/jhootha-kahin-ka-et00105933-27-06-2019-07-04-59.jpg";			function fnChangeUrl(pathName) {
				try {
					var myURL = window.location.pathname.substr(0, window.location.pathname.indexOf("movies"));
					window.location = myURL+"movies/"+pathName;
				} catch(e) {
					BMS.Misc.fnErr({ fnName : "fnChangeUrl", err : e });
				}

                        						<div id="mv-summary" class="tab-content" style="display: none;">
                                                    <div class="__heading">SYNOPSIS</div>
                            <div class="synopsis">
                               <blockquote cite="http://in.bookmyshow.com/movies/jhootha-kahin-ka/ET00105933">
									
 When Varun meets Riya at a wedding, it`s love at first sight for him. Willing to go to any length for the love of Riya, Varun lies about being an orphan. The two soon get married, but things take an unexpected turn when his parents and Riya`s family end up as neighbours! How much longer can Varun keep the lie alive before everything goes awry?								</blockquote>
                            </div>

	<span class="__timestamp">19/7/19</span>									  </span></div><div class="__reviewer-text">Smeep Kang's "Jhoota Kahin Ka", is a Bollywood comedy-drama. The film can very well be watched and enjoyed with your friends and family. The movie gives you an outburst of comedy after the intermission leaving you with  laughter in the end.
It was a sight to sore eyes to watch Rishi ji after a long time on screen, and he surely surprised us with his comic timing. About the Pyaar ka Punchnama boys being back. Well, they really are with a bang. Although the movie takes a slow start but Jimmy's dialogues post his entry will keep you  hooked to your seats
The music is good but the icing on the cake is Sunny leone and Honey Singh's 'Funk love'. Over all the movie is worth a watch.</div></div></div><div class="mv-synopsis-review"><div class="__reviewer-face"><div class="wow __reviewer-image-area" style="visibility: visible;"><img <script type="text/javascript">
  if ( BMS.Storage.get({name:"ld", "key":"MEMBERID", storage: "C"}) != "" ) {
    if (typeof(clevertap) !== "undefined") {
      clevertap.profile.push({
